drm/i915: Add PIPE_CONF_CHECK_CLOCK_FUZZY()

Add a new pipe config check macro PIPE_CONF_CHECK_CLOCK_FUZZY() to make
it trivial and error proof to compare clocks in a fuzzy manner.

v2: Drop extra curly braces

